<p style="text-align: justify;">Periodicity – 4 issues per year.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The target audience of the journal is made up of researchers, lecturers who study sociological problems of modern society on a theoretical and empirical level. The journal is addressed to experts of sociological and information-analytical services of state and public organizations, commercial structures. The journal is directed towards postgraduate students, applicants, master’s degree students and students of social and humanitarian profile, as well as all those who are interested in social problems of the development and functioning of society.</p>
